In the Matter of Michael TEMPLOME and Carolina Templome individually and as Copartners Doing Business under the Firm Name of Michael Templome and Carolina Templome, Bankrupts-Appellants, v. Vincent VANSHURA and Agnes Vanshura, Objecting CreditorsAppellees. No. 43. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Nov. 4, 1935. Pratt & Lichtig, of New York City (David M. Berger, of New York City, of counsel), for appellants. James A. O’Gorman, Jr., of New York City (Francis X. Nicastro, of New York City, of counsel), for appellees.

Before MANTON, AUGUSTUS N. HAND, and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Order affirmed.
